text.tspan: User Testing for the Rest of US

flowRoot.flowPara: Cantarell is the default UI font in GNOME3. The founder of the project, Dave Crossland, details his work during the last few years to cultivate a free culture of typography, and reveals a new model of crowdfunding that he hopes will enable more people to work on their projects full time.
Keynote: Making Free Fonts Full Time -- Main Auditorium, 9 a.m.
